<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link71892" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=71892&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F162760-this-book-is-full-of-revisionist-history%2Fanswers%2F71892-follett-has-a-left">flag</a>
</div>
<ul class='communityQAFooter answerFooter'>
