<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I agree with Sarah, I think it&apos;s quite well known that he really did have a number of affairs. I believe Maria&apos;s story is loosely based on the true st<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I agree with Sarah, I think it's quite well known that he really did have a number of affairs. I believe Maria's story is loosely based on the true story of Mimi Alford, a White House intern who had an affair with JFK. <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mimi_Alford">http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mimi_A...</a><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
